rating_comment: The host is a very kind person,the place is really beautiful and well decorated as well!

The host was always caring and proactive to communicate. Both the property owner and manager are smart and gentleman. They always tried to help us. We felt like home. Though the checkout time was 11:00 Am but they alowed us to stay whole day. I highly recommend this house for peaceful guests.
The place is roomy, with excellent amenities, including furnishings. Though the host is new, they're eager to go the extra mile for guests. We had a delightful stay.
